English
After trying everything to get his wife Audrey (Olivia Munn) pregnant, Tommy
Macklin (Paul Schneider) realizes to his horror that he may be "shooting
blanks." Terrified that his marriage may fall apart, Tommy recruits his
friends (and an Indian ex-mobster) to rob a sperm bank where he made a deposit
years ago. As with any half-baked scheme, everything can and does go wrong,
testing the limits of Tommy and Audrey's relationship. The Babymakers is a
hilarious twist on the heist film genre, a laugh-out loud comedy showing how
far one couple will go in hopes of creating a new life.
